# engineerbunny

The goal of engineerbunny is to facilitate data engineering.

## Installation

You can install the development version of engineerbunny from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("DanielBraddock/engineerbunny")
```
